                      Capa L3 con 24 puertos Gigabit PoE+ (370W)
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 text-sm text-blue-200">
                      <span class="flex items-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-microchip mr-2"></i>
                        Modelo: C9200L-24P-4G-E
                      </span>
                      <span class="flex items-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-bolt mr-2"></i>
                        370W PoE+
                      </span>
                      <span class="flex items-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-network-wired mr-2"></i>
                        56 Gbps
                      </span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  
                  <!-- Badge de disponibilidad -->
                  <div class="hidden md:block">
                    <div class="bg-green-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold flex items-center">
                      <i class="fas fa-check-circle mr-2"></i>
                      Disponible
                    </div>
                  </div>
